<p>
<h1>Wiz Quiz!</h1>
</p>
<p>
With the slightly cold atmosphere in The Land of late, and a distinct shortage of more visible wizards and witches, I decided that perhaps the MUDII populace of today might benefit from getting to know their wizzes a little better. A legendarily ornery and secretive lot, the best way to get answers from them would be a short series of questions sent to them all, with a little assistance (and a lot of pestering) from the ever-helpful Karya. 
</p>
<p>
And here are the results - a surprising 16 wizards graced us with their responses, from the old school to the present day, although sadly some of our current active wizards haven't made the roster (perhaps too busy killing mages, eh? *sniff*). Through the use of elite surveillance equipment secreted within the wizroom, I've even managed to obtain photographs of the wizards in their natural state - tremble in fear at their visages! 
</p>
<p>
Without further ado, and in alphabetical order - onwards!
</p>
<p>
<p><h3>AGRAZAG</h3>
</p>
<p><img align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10" src="issue/23/images/agrazag1.gif">
<i>1) Your favourite prefix is...</i>
<br>
<br>
tetchy 
<br>
<br>
<i>2) Where are you now?</i>
<br>
<br>
Ummm ... at home!
<br>
<br>
<i>3) How did you make wiz?</i>
<br>
<br>
By surviving Dunbad for long enough to score however many points it is you need ... and finally
swamping the crown.
<br>
<br>
<i>4) In real life, you are...</i>
<br>
<br>
Tetchy
<br>
<br>
<i>5) Tell us something we didn't know about you...</i>
<br>
<br>
I hate being asked awkward questions!
</p>
<p align=center>
-----------
</p>
<p><h3>AZRAEL</h3>
</p>
<p><img align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10" src="issue/23/images/azrael1.gif">
<i>1) Your favourite prefix is...</i>
<br>
<br>
Demonic. What do you mean I'm not giving you any information that QW doesn't? 
<br>
<br>
<i>2) Where are you now?</i>
<br>
<br>
In a ditch, covered in petrol, on fire, somewhere near Albuquerque. 
<br>
<br>
<i>3) How did you make wiz?</i>
<br>
<br>
Short answer, by entering the fountain. Long answer, check the back issues of Muddled Times circa July 2001. 
<br>
<br>
<i>4) In real life, you are...</i>
<br>
<br>
The grand despot of a small unpronounceable eastern European country. But living in a ditch somewhere near Albuquerque. Oh yes, consistency is beneath me. 
<br>
<br>
<i>5) Tell us something we didn't know about you...</i>
<br>
<br>
When I was nine I was shot dead by a hamster. I got better, although I now hold a lifelong grudge against my former assailant.
</p>
