<br>
<br>
<i>4) In real life, you are...</i>
<br>
<br>
In real life I'm the lord of an underground goat liberation organisation who go to farms and spray logos on their walls and defecate in their wellies. I also like to ski.
<br>
<br>
<i>5) Tell us something we didn't know about you...</i>
<br>
<br>
Since I was a small child my auntie has called me Willy Bum Fairy (my name is Will) and until a few months ago I didn't realise that she's been insinuating that I was a homosexual. I need to have words.
</p>
